\&#039;Diary Of An Afro Warrior\&#039; is the debut album by the much-vaunted dubstep visionary Benga. A dark collection of sparse dubstep beats that owes a debt to Mantronix, Goldie and Dizzee Rascal, this sterling selection will also appeal to fans of Burial.
